These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball, badminton, biathlon, handball
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, rock, disco, metal, folk
 1. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the fan of salsa is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of disco##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the chinese and the person who's sport is handball##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Sport   | badminton     | volleyball      | biathlon | handball   | swimming    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Music-Genre           | rock | disco      | folk     | metal   | salsa     |

