.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, july, april, february, may
5 different games are played: bridge, go, scrabble, snooker, billiard
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the chinese and the person playing billiard##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the indian is the person playing snooker##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing go##1
11. the indian is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Birthday         | february | june | may    | july  | april    |
| Game   | billiard    | go       | scrabble      | bridge | snooker        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

