.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, old-henry, baccarat, chaman, fonseca
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, september, march, june, november
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the old-henry-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
13. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Cigar   | baccarat      | old-henry      | chaman       | fonseca       | alhambra       |
| Birthday         | september | november  | june    | october    | march        |

