.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, swisher, baccarat, game, cain
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking
City: boston, san-francisco, miami, colone, edinburgh
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 3. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person traveling to colone and the game-smoker##2
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to colone is the british##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the british is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
13. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Cigar          | cain  | baccarat     | game   | swisher     | prince |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking    | singing  | skydiving | puzzles   |
| City   | san-francisco        | boston    | edinburgh     | miami     | colone    |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | indonesian | japanese | pakistani | british   |

