.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, action, family, musical, superhero
There 5 different types of food: apricot, broccoli, lettuce, orange, watermelon
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, aristoff, ritmeester, cain, alhambra
 1. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 4. the person watching family movies is between the aristoff-smoker and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 9. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
10. the person watching action movies is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical       | superhero       | drama   | family      | action    |
| Food       | watermelon | orange        | apricot       | lettuce       | broccoli |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| Cigar      | cain | ritmeester | oliveros      | alhambra | aristoff  |

