.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite, water
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, blue, ivory, apricot, green
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, snowmobile, taxi, motorbike
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, rowing, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the person who likes green and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes green and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
13. the person who likes green is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | water      | sprite   | fanta   | soy-milk   |
| Color   | green    | apricot   | ivory   | blue | chestnut     |
| Transport   | jet-ski | snowmobile     | taxi   | motorbike | scooter |
| Sport         | badminton | volleyball | baseball | rowing  | skiing     |

