5 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, horse, pony, rat
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, peas, cucumber, broccoli, apricot
 1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the rat is the person eating peas##1
 4. the owner of the horse is between the person watching crime movies and the egyptian##2
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is in the middle##1
 7. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the turkish##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the right of the colombian##1
12. the owner of the dog is the person watching spy movies##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
