.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, begonia, rose, sunflower, lily
There 5 different types of food: watermelon, apricot, pepper, carrot, pomegranate
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train, trike, van
 1. the person eating pomegranate is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person eating apricot##2
 2. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growssunflower##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
10. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person eating pepper and the person who growsrose##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who growslily##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Flower       | lily | aconite | rose  | sunflower | begonia    |
| Food       | pepper        | carrot   | apricot  | pomegranate   | watermelon |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

