.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
There 5 different types of food: cranberry, eggplant, kale, mango, pear
House: cape-cod, townhouse, cottage, gothic-revival, colonial
 1. the cottage house is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person eating kale and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the fisherman##1
 4. the person eating pear is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 5. the person eating cranberry is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the pilot and the townhouse house##2
 7. the gothic-revival house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the cottage house##1
 9. the cape-cod house is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person eating eggplant##1
12. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Job           | engineer | entrepreneur | fisherman | pilot    | bartender  |
| Food   | mango  | eggplant    | cranberry | kale    | pear |
| House   | cottage  | townhouse        | cape-cod   | gothic-revival    | colonial     |

