 6. the american is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person playing monopoly and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is chessd-games##2
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is chessd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is chessd-games is on the right of the indonesian##1

