There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, grey, aquamarine, black, emerald
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is between the malaysian and the person who likes emerald##2
 3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is the person who likes ivory##1
 5. the person who likes ivory is between the thai and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person drinking tea is the person who likes black##1
 8. the person who's hobby is emerald-climbing is the person who likes grey##1
 9. the american is the person who likes grey##1
10. the person who's hobby is emerald-climbing is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | emerald-climbing |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | lemonade   | cola | tea | 7up   |
| Color   | aquamarine | ivory    | emerald    | black       | grey         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 